author: Caille Millner
title: Ocean Beach bonfires? Sure. $35 fee? No way!
text:
Photo: Franchon Smith, The Chronicle Emaly Torres, 21, of Lafayette and Omar Reynoso, 22, of Vallejo spend their evening at San Francisco's Ocean Beach enjoying a bonfire on October 17, 2015. Emaly Torres, 21, of Lafayette and Omar Reynoso, 22, of Vallejo...
During my brief moments of teenage delinquency, I remember late nights that ended triumphantly at Ocean Beach, passing joints and listening to some kid strum a guitar badly around a bonfire.
